Titolo: Crashmo

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Crashmo, known as Fallblox in Europe and Australia and as Hiku Otsu in Japan, is a puzzle video game developed by Intelligent Systems and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo 3DS via the Nintendo eShop. The game is a sequel to Pushmo and was released in Japan on October 31, 2012, in Europe and Australia on November 15, 2012, and in North America on November 22, 2012.
In Crashmo, players controls Mallo who goes across the Crashmo Park and solve Crashmos at a request.
The game received praise for its graphics and new features, although its high level of difficulty received mixed opinions. Two sequels, Pushmo World for the Wii U and Stretchmo for the Nintendo 3DS were released in 2014 and 2015 respectively.

